This project demonstrates how OpenCV can be used to perform real-time colour-based object detection, a foundational technique in robotic vision. Such methods are widely applied in autonomous robots, surveillance systems, and human-robot interaction**, making OpenCV an essential tool in modern robotics and computer vision research.

